Raw anglerfish are a type of fish found only in Port Piscarilius. In order to catch this fish, players require level 82 in Fishing, 100% Piscarilius favour, a fishing rod, and sandworms. Each catch grants 120 Fishing experience. Anglerfish are located at the bait fishing spot south of Tynan's Fishing Supplies.

Cooking anglerfish requires level 84 in Cooking, and gives 230 experience. Burning anglerfish will result in a burnt anglerfish. The amount of Hitpoints healed is dependent on the player's Hitpoints level. At level 93, an anglerfish will heal 22. Anglerfish can also heal above maximum Hitpoints (making the maximum Hitpoints possible 121).
